disp_name.description:
Name of the ability
Only necessary if the value differs from Fey Feathers.

description.value: Innate: Rakan periodically generates a 33 − 254 (based on level) (+ 90% AP) shield that lasts until broken. If the shield is damaged, but not destroyed after being out of combat for 5 seconds, it will regenerate 10% of its maximum value every second.

description2.value: Basic attacks and abilities reduce Fey Feathers'  cooldown by 1 second for each enemy champion hit.

description3.value: Innate - Lover's Leap: If either Rakan or Xayah is channeling Recall, the other may move nearby and channel their own to join them. Both reach base at the time of which the initiator's recall ends.

targeting.description: Permafrost is a single target ability.

affects.description: Permafrost affects enemy champions and large monsters

onhiteffects.description: onhiteffects can be set to 'true', for abilities that apply on-hit effects (from items or other abilities)

occurrence.description: occurrence can either be set to 'hit' or 'attack', and refers to on-hit effects

spellshield.description: spellshield can either be set to true, or written with a custom description.

callforhelp.description: callforhelp determines whether minion aggro will transfer to the caster

additional.description: Displays additional information in a smaller window below the template.

notes.value: * Revitalize will record bonus shielding when a new shield is created, but not when it regenerates. In either case, there is no bonus shielding received. The cooldown reduction is granted even if the ability is blocked by a spell shield.
notes.description: Displays additional information with effect table to the right.

disp_name.description:
Name of the ability
Only necessary if the value differs from Gleaming Quill.

blurb.value: Flings a magical feather that deals magic damage. Striking a champion or epic monster enables Rakan to heal his allies.

description.value: Active: Rakan slings an enchanted feather in the target direction, dealing magic damage to the first enemy hit.

description2.value: If the target was an enemy champion or epic monster, an area is marked around Rakan.

description3.value: After 3 seconds or if an ally champion comes within the marked area, Rakan heals himself and surrounding allies for 18 − 120 (based on level) (+ 70% AP).

disp_name.description:
Name of the ability
Only necessary if the value differs from Grand Entrance.

blurb.value: Dashes to a location, knocking up nearby enemies on arrival.

description.value: Active: Rakan dashes to the target location.

description2.value: After a 0.35-second delay upon arrival, he leaps into the air, dealing magic damage and knocking up surrounding enemies for 1 second.

description3.value: Rakan will be knocked down by any immobilizing crowd control during Grand Entrance.

description4.value: Grand Entrance will cast at max range if cast beyond that.

disp_name.description:
Name of the ability
Only necessary if the value differs from Battle Dance.

blurb.value: Flies to an allied champion granting them a shield. Can be re-cast for free for a short duration.

description.value: Active: Rakan shields the target allied champion for 3 seconds and then dashes to and around them. Battle Dance can be recast within 5 seconds without a cost at no delay.

description2.value: Recast: Rakan mimics the first cast's effects.

description3.value: Rakan will be knocked down by any immobilizing crowd control during Battle Dance.

description4.value: If Xayah is the target, Battle Dance can be cast from an increased range.

notes.value: *Both casts count as ability activations for the purposes of on-cast effects such as Spellblade, charging Spellbinder, and stacking Force Pulse. The shields do not stack if Battle Dance is cast on the same target twice. Only the duration and shield amount is refreshed.

disp_name.description:
Name of the ability
Only necessary if the value differs from The Quickness.

blurb.value: Gains movement speed, charming and dealing magic damage to enemies touched.

description.value: Active: Rakan breaks into a captivating sprint for 4 seconds, gaining  75% bonus movement speed and becoming ghosted for the duration. During this time he deals magic damage to all enemy units he collides with, in addition to charming and slowing them by 75%. Colliding with an enemy champion increases The Quickness' duration by 0.25 seconds. This may only occur once per champion.

description2.value: When Rakan collides with his first enemy champion he gains an additional  75% bonus movement speed, which starts decaying after 0.5 seconds by 20% every 0.5 seconds and then by 15% after decaying by 60% over 1.5 seconds.

description3.value: During the first 0.5 seconds of The Quickness, Rakan is in cast time.

description4.value: During The Quickness, Rakan cannot basic attack enemy champions if he did not charm them, unless the attack command was inputted before the ability was activated.
